  "description": "<h3><strong>Medical Social Worker (5-Month Contract)</strong></h3><p><strong>Location:</strong> Jurong East Govt <br /> <strong>Start Date:</strong> Mar 2026 ( ongoing interview now ) <br /> <strong>Duration:</strong> 5 Months<br /> <strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> Up to $5,000 (commensurate with experience)<br /> <strong>Employment Type:</strong> Contract (Office Hours)</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li>Conduct comprehensive bio-psychosocial assessments and provide appropriate interventions in line with best clinical practices</li><li>Deliver specialised clinical care directly to patients and families</li><li>Supervise and evaluate the performance of Medical Social Workers, Executives, and support staff</li><li>Lead or participate in assigned clinical and service-related projects</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li>Degree or postgraduate qualification in Social Work</li><li>Social Worker Keen in Medical Social Worker welcome to apply </li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p><p><strong>Email : </strong><a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></a></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
